{"tid":49981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【好狠心】「聖戰母親」吻別兩幼女 送她們當人肉炸彈","createTime":"2016-12-22T05:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T05:47:34.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31ca94e1f7690b3da13510674a1dd3edb2592fd1","tid":49981,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T05:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161222/large/1482351707_bc2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161222%2Flarge%2F1482351707_bc2c.jpg&h=bc3f7e15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上日前流傳片段，據稱是敍利亞一對將擔當人肉炸彈的姊妹，與父母離別時的一刻。<br />\n片段中的女童分別7歲和9歲，被穿罩袍的媽媽擁抱和吻別後，接受一名鬍鬚男子「洗腦」，學習如何執行自殺式任務。<br />\n<br />\n這段片拍攝後，7歲妹妹上周被派到敍利亞首都大馬士革，以借洗手間之名，進入一間警局後，她身上的遙控炸彈就爆炸。她當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n暫時未知哪個組織下令發動這次襲擊，但當地傳媒報道，女童父親是「敍利亞征服陣線」（Jabhat Fateh al-Sham）成員。該組織由阿蓋德分支「勝利陣線」改組而成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161222/56077223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161222%2F56077223&d=oWaruqJxbgGKsQHa%2FbqJqZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=734f733c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161222%2F56077223&h=cde4c71a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161222/56077223</a>"},{"pid":"052bc5fab2b8354efc9562a37fd0dd795bea958f","tid":49981,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:09:23.000Z","msg":"男人就話上到天堂有72個處女，女人就俾人72連發<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9c70633ff2793df74cd17acca3c9bb91919181","tid":49981,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad43818b6139025ba945efdfa641888918ae29f","tid":4998